reviews.title: Misleading listing
reviews.review: The item listed is one and item shipped to me were completely different CPU. The CPU that I received was 10920x which just has 12 cores. The Item listed is 10980xe which has 18 cores 48 PCIE lanes etc. When I demanded for replacement they tried to give me a refund. I was not satisfied with the response because if they had the version listed in the website. They would sent a replacement. So my recommendation is don't buy from this listing since they have messed up so many times.
